html:
  - !DEF [TITLE, '{TITLE}/about']
  - !DEF [SUBTITLE, '']
  - !DEF [FOOTER_NAME, about]
  - !INCLUDE /blocks/head.block
  - body:
      - !DEF [TITLE_FLAVOUR_ID, about-flavour]
      - !INCLUDE /blocks/footer.block
      - !INCLUDE /blocks/title.block
      - div:
          - h1: Who
          - p: I go by 'theokrueger'. I am interested in cooking, baking, and computer systems. This site is content-driven rather than personality-driven.
          - p:
              - 'Anything else that would be included here can instead be found by viewing either my '
              - a:
                  - _href: '/portfolio'
                  - Portfolio
              - ' or my '
              - a:
                  - _href: '/posts'
                  - Posts
              - '.'
          - p:
              - 'You can contact me through email at '
              - a:
                  _href: 'mailto:{CONTACT_INFO}'
                  t: '{CONTACT_INFO}'
      - div:
          - h1: What
          - p: I try to only post interesting or interactive things, which inevitably leads to inactivity. Almost everything will be computer-related because that is how I spend my free time.
      - div:
          - h1: How
          - p:
              - 'Built using '
              - a:
                  _href: 'https://crates.io/crates/ssgen'
                  t: '{SSGEN_VERSION}'
          - p:
              - 'Styled after Emacs and the deprecated '
              - a:
                  _href: 'https://git.savannah.gnu.org/cgit/emacs.git/tree/etc/themes/light-blue-theme.el'
                  t: 'light-blue-theme.el'
          - p:
              - 'View the source code for this page '
              - a:
                  _href: '{SITE_SOURCE}'
                  t: here
              - '.'
          - p:
              - 'By browsing (or scraping) this site, you agree to the '
              - a:
                  _href: '/assets/TOS.txt'
                  _target: '_blank'
                  t: 'Terms of Service'
              - ' (real).'
